commentTextItems.html: straight drive, throw at the keepers end deflects of the batsman and stops just short of teh boundary, Canada didn't run, I doubt Kevin O'Brien would have done the same

commentPostTextItems.html: And we are past the cut off time, Umpires have called it off, Canada are ahead on D/L.
Canada wins the game by 4 runs, brilliant effort from the men in red

commentTextItems.html: Zubin puts into the gap between point and cover
cuts through him, this is TJs last over, Dockrell and O'Brien are done as well

lofts if over mid on, for a double

commentPostTextItems.html: D/L Par Score 159, Canada 160, 16 in 18 for the complete game

commentTextItems.html: bouncer too high, keeper misses it too
quick from kevin and then goes and mouths of to the batsman
trying to slap it past point misses it completely

dismissalText.commentary: Ruvindu Gunasekera c White b O'Brien 71 (95b 6x4 0x6 132m) SR: 74.73

commentTextItems.html: gone, tried to scoop it plays it straight to short fine leg, Kevin gives him a send off, trying to take something away from a wonderful knock, the crowd boes, him, but never the less Game back into balance
inside edge, to short fine leg, and they scamper a single
late cut to third man for another single

commentPostTextItems.html: Par Score is 151, 22 of 4 overs if the game goes the distance

commentTextItems.html: single to mid wicket on that yorker
defends it to point and takes off
never a run there, direct hit would have swung this match around, he just dabbed it to mid off and took off
flicked to mdi wicket for a single

commentPostTextItems.html: 26 in 30 and if it gets too dark or rains Canada needs to be at 137 right now adn 144 by the end of the next over
